    <CMUI_Label name="lblHeading" id="b84eceb5-6702-473d-be76-212e20eb781b">
        <alignment>1</alignment>
        <caption>This option allows data on the cargo to be updated onto the transaction, and then the transaction is resynched through the transactions map.

The current values are shown. If the data on the transaction is different the transaction's value is shown in red. Select the data that requires updating onto the transaction.

Selecting an attribute to be updated is not mandatory. Clicking Save will resynch anyway.

Break-bulk or bulk cargo that has been split cannot update the quantity, weight or volume onto the transaction.</caption>
        <transparent/>
        <wordWrap/>
        <fontSize>8.25</fontSize>
        <foreColor>-2147483640</foreColor>
        <parent name="CMUI_TransactionResync"/>
        <parentBottomOffset>624</parentBottomOffset>
        <parentRightOffset>14</parentRightOffset>
        <show3D>3</show3D>
        <tabIndex>9266</tabIndex>
        <backColor>-2147483633</backColor>
        <enabled/>
        <height>190</height>
        <left>12</left>
        <top>9</top>
        <visible/>
        <width>477</width>
    </CMUI_Label>
